while whatever knowledge we have in
the colleges, Medical College,

00:00:40.714 --> 00:00:45.404
Colleges of Psychology and Other
Sciences, which deal with

00:00:45.404 --> 00:00:53.632
human-beings on Scientific Research
and Scientific Datas, is the knowledge
of the tree.

