With human awareness we cannot
dive down into ourselves.

00:01:09.746 --> 00:01:14.249
For example, you are all paying
attention to Me but if I say that,

00:01:14.249 --> 00:01:17.210
take your attention inside,
you cannot take it.

00:01:17.210 --> 00:01:23.794
You'll say, "How to do it? It doesn't go
inside." Our attention is spread outside
- that is how we are made.

00:01:23.794 --> 00:01:32.528
Specially, that we should put our
attention outside and understand
the value of our feedom.

00:01:33.113 --> 00:01:39.543
As human-beings we are free to
choose right and wrong.

00:01:40.433 --> 00:01:47.893
We have through traditions developed
lot of correct ideas about right
and wrong

00:01:48.280 --> 00:01:55.740
but there have been lots of saints
and seers who have given us

00:01:56.721 --> 00:02:01.501
a complete idea about what is right
and what is wrong.

00:02:02.123 --> 00:02:14.283
Despite that, we find it difficult to be
righteous, to be virtuous, to be what
that we believe in.

00:02:14.852 --> 00:02:21.382
We see something, we hear something,
we know something, that it is good
that we should be like that,

00:02:21.382 --> 00:02:31.533
but we just can't do it. We're not
'samarth', we're not capable of doing
what we believe.

00:02:31.746 --> 00:02:38.836
The reason for this is because we are
not integrated personalities.

00:02:39.596 --> 00:02:45.846
Our brain says something, our heart
says another thing and our liver
does another thing.

00:02:45.846 --> 00:02:53.381
So we are divided into three, four
personalities and that's why we
cannot integrate ourselves.

00:02:53.771 --> 00:03:00.381
To integrate ourselves, we have to
become something that is integrated
within ourselves.

00:03:00.381 --> 00:03:09.490
Now this integrated self is the Spirit.
The Spirit resides in the heart.

00:03:09.760 --> 00:03:15.360
It is said by all the seers but in Sahaja
yoga, now we can prove it that it
does reside.

00:03:15.360 --> 00:03:21.907
That is, God Almighty reflects Himself
in the heart, as Spirit.

00:03:21.907 --> 00:03:27.859
And the Spirit is the One, which is
watching us all the time.

00:03:28.429 --> 00:03:33.989
The Spirit does not manifest in our
attention. If it starts manifesting

00:03:33.989 --> 00:03:39.208
in our attention, then we start feeling
on our Central Nervous System,

00:03:40.742 --> 00:03:47.332
the coolness of the Spirit, the vibrations
of the Spirit, the manifestation
of the Spirit.

00:03:47.332 --> 00:03:53.276
But when it does not manifest, it keeps
out and watches us as a Saakshi.

00:03:53.446 --> 00:03:59.376
Now, this Spirit is the One, that is
the integrated point.

00:03:59.527 --> 00:04:03.967
Once we become the Spirit all these
beings that are within us

00:04:03.967 --> 00:04:07.849
which are disintegrated become
completely integrated

00:04:07.849 --> 00:04:15.484
and that's how we become capable of
doing what we believe good or right

00:04:15.575 --> 00:04:22.350
through our mind, through our efforts
and through our love.

00:04:22.350 --> 00:04:32.387
It all combines together and we do
perform everything that has complete
integrated expression.

00:04:33.506 --> 00:04:40.906
Now to become the Spirit, people have
said that you have to meditate, you
have to go inside

00:04:41.360 --> 00:04:46.296
because at the time of Shri Krishna,
He could not talk on these level

00:04:46.296 --> 00:04:49.514
that people were not so well-equipped
to understand it.

00:04:51.810 --> 00:04:53.841
Now how to meditate,
is again the problem.

00:04:53.995 --> 00:04:58.915
If I say, you have to go inside to
meditate, you'll say how to go inside?

00:04:59.156 --> 00:05:05.126
Now, we have to understand, God
Almighty has made us very beautifully.

00:05:05.738 --> 00:05:10.138
We never ask the question once, "Why
has He made us a human-being?"

00:05:10.138 --> 00:05:15.968
"Why did we go through the complete
process of evolution to become
a human-being?"

00:05:15.976 --> 00:05:20.966
Now we have become a human-being
but why, why are we human-being?

00:05:20.966 --> 00:05:25.750
And if human-beings are the epitome
of evolution,

00:05:25.750 --> 00:05:29.834
then why there are problems, why
we are not integrated?

00:05:29.834 --> 00:05:36.587
So, we have to jump a little higher
stage, a little higher awareness

00:05:36.587 --> 00:05:40.640
by which we start understanding
the Absolute nature.

00:05:40.744 --> 00:05:45.644
Just now we are living on absolutely
relative terminology.

00:05:45.712 --> 00:05:50.832
Everything is relative. You don't know
whether this is good or bad, whether
this should be done or not?

00:05:50.832 --> 00:05:55.329
But for a self-realized person there is
no doubt because he knows

00:05:55.329 --> 00:06:02.976
that his Spirit is emitting those
vibrations, which are all the time flowing

00:06:02.976 --> 00:06:06.795
and if he tries to do something wrong,
they immediately stop.

00:06:07.115 --> 00:06:14.942
So, like a computer he gets attached or
you can say, united with the Divine

00:06:14.942 --> 00:06:22.173
and then the computer starts working
and informing that this is not right
and that is not right.

00:06:22.482 --> 00:06:32.632
It's a very wonderful computer that God
has created; We are one of the most
exceptional type of computers.

00:06:32.695 --> 00:06:36.280
We have computers in the world that
human-beings have created

00:06:36.280 --> 00:06:40.458
it has to go through the thinking
power and then come to something

00:06:40.464 --> 00:06:47.164
and the thinking is also fed into it by
another thinking one, who has thought
from a very limited energy.

00:06:47.919 --> 00:06:55.679
But we do not think and we see. I see
you without thinking, I can see
you without thinking.

00:06:55.686 --> 00:07:00.916
As soon as I see you, I know who
you are but for a computer,

00:07:00.916 --> 00:07:05.812
it has to go through the process of
finding out who the person is.

00:07:05.812 --> 00:07:14.666
Now, there's a big challenge now facing
us that people are taking to artificial
methods in every field of life

00:07:14.708 --> 00:07:20.348
because they have not been able to go
higher than what they are,

00:07:20.348 --> 00:07:25.533
because they have missed their ascent,
they're taking to all kinds of artificial
things.

00:07:25.533 --> 00:07:30.336
First of all they are taking to artificial
things like computers.

00:07:30.905 --> 00:07:39.135
Now these computers could be very
dangerous because the matter is all the
time trying to overpower the Spirit.

00:07:39.135 --> 00:07:45.906
When you are creating a machine, you
don't know how much you are going in
the clutches of the machinery.

00:07:45.906 --> 00:07:51.692
That the machine one day, if you do
not allow and assert your freedom

00:07:51.692 --> 00:07:56.832
and a proportionate understanding of
the powers of machine also,

00:07:56.832 --> 00:08:00.700
you might just be finished
completely.

00:08:00.700 --> 00:08:04.970
You can see that these computers
now can speak, can take over.

00:08:04.970 --> 00:08:09.154
Supposing something goes wrong with
the computer, it can start devouring

00:08:09.154 --> 00:08:14.825
the whole world - how can you stop it?
Because, it's a machine, it's the matter

00:08:14.825 --> 00:08:21.175
which is, which doesn't understand - it
is innocent. It doesn't understand
whether it is constructing or destroying.

00:08:21.562 --> 00:08:28.902
So, this is a very dangerous point where
we have arrived. In every field we are
doing such dangerous things.

00:08:28.966 --> 00:08:36.486
Like in the agricultural side we can see
that we try to make a hybrid seed;

00:08:36.592 --> 00:08:43.452
Hybrid seed can never produce seeds.
Moreover the all this hybrid business
gives problems.

00:08:43.702 --> 00:08:47.912
If you study a hybrid cow and an
ordinary cow, you'll be amazed

00:08:47.912 --> 00:08:52.877
that the hybrid cow has no sensitivity
to her child.

00:08:53.411 --> 00:09:01.421
If she, if a calf dies of a simple cow, she
stops giving milk, she stops giving milk

00:09:01.520 --> 00:09:07.680
because her love informs her that the
child is no more - what is the use of
giving milk now, for whom?

00:09:07.708 --> 00:09:12.628
But if a hybrid cow's calf dies,
this doesn't bother her.

00:09:13.283 --> 00:09:19.693
You see the little hen that we have
in the villages - because people have
now studied them very well -

00:09:19.715 --> 00:09:24.185
they say, a hen, which is an ordinary
hen, which is a normal hen,

00:09:24.185 --> 00:09:29.295
if it sees the little chicks around
it and when the, she sees the

00:09:29.746 --> 00:09:36.460
some sort of an attack from some birds
or something, she immediately calls her

00:09:36.460 --> 00:09:43.159
little chicks and puts her, her complete
protection for them.

00:09:43.573 --> 00:09:52.233
But if you have somebody, say a,
somebody which is a hybrid one

00:09:52.469 --> 00:09:57.160
like the incubator or something - they
have no feeling for their children,

00:09:57.160 --> 00:10:00.895
they have no feeling for them, so even if
some rat is coming - anything -

00:10:00.895 --> 00:10:04.690
she is not bothered - let somebody eat
the children, do what they like.

00:10:05.510 --> 00:10:12.331
It is so much going into our lives that
we are not aware as to how much we
are dominated by the matter.

00:10:12.366 --> 00:10:21.996
Matter is a very important thing but it is
to be seen what it does to the Spirit.

00:10:22.930 --> 00:10:27.710
Now for example, what we do of matter,
is nothing but to change it's forms.

00:10:27.710 --> 00:10:31.680
We develop an ego thinking, 'We have
done this, we have done that,

00:10:31.680 --> 00:10:37.715
we have built this big thing and we have
huge, big palaces built by us."

00:10:37.715 --> 00:10:42.416
But what are all these things - are
nothing but stones - from dead
to the dead.

00:10:42.416 --> 00:10:46.069
What have you achieved? Nothing but
an ego, which is absolutely

00:10:46.069 --> 00:10:49.445
- ego means something you believe
into which does not exist.

00:10:49.445 --> 00:10:57.180
So you believe into something that is
the matter, that you have changed the
forms of the matter

00:10:57.180 --> 00:11:00.573
but as a result what happens, you
become a slave of the matter.

00:11:00.573 --> 00:11:04.212
For example, those who are used to the
chair, cannot sit on the ground.

00:11:04.582 --> 00:11:10.722
You get used to it, you form habits and
this matter starts dominating you
all the time.

00:11:10.722 --> 00:11:15.202
When the whole ideology in the West
starts with the individual growth

00:11:15.202 --> 00:11:20.607
and also of the comfort - comfort is a
very important thing in the
Western philosophy

