that if you want to have anything
that is simple, that is natural,

00:12:02.167 --> 00:12:09.200
you just can't get it. You have to do the
way it is done for the whole there and
that's what you have to accept.

00:12:09.200 --> 00:12:15.367
While in India, thank God, we are not
that mad, that we still can get lots
of things which are fresh.

00:12:15.367 --> 00:12:21.090
But the greatest thing we can get in
this world is the love, love of
other people.

00:12:21.090 --> 00:12:26.132
Holi is one of the festivals in which we
express our love to all the people.

00:12:26.132 --> 00:12:30.342
Now, in England if you go or in any
other Western countries,

00:12:30.342 --> 00:12:35.913
the love is expressed through a printed
card, where we say, "We wish you a
happy Christmas," - finished.

00:12:35.913 --> 00:12:39.950
To their father also they send a card,
"We wish you a happy Christmas."

00:12:39.950 --> 00:12:46.160
You go to the market, get some papers,
write down or they might get
readymade everything.

00:12:46.160 --> 00:12:48.786
You get readymade for the mother,
readymade for the father,

00:12:48.786 --> 00:12:51.381
readymade for the grandfather,
readymade for everything.

00:12:51.381 --> 00:12:54.820
Just bring the readymade stuff and
write it down and send it over.

00:12:54.820 --> 00:13:02.224
I've seen sometimes people make
mistakes and they might send a, one of

00:13:02.224 --> 00:13:06.397
these readymade ones in such a funny
way, that instead of addressing

00:13:06.397 --> 00:13:09.250
to the child, they may address it
to the grandmother.

00:13:09.250 --> 00:13:18.499
So, it is so much of a mechanized life
that you have lost that flexibility,

00:13:18.499 --> 00:13:22.694
that can really inspire love within
our hearts.

00:13:22.694 --> 00:13:27.453
Such people become absolutely dry,
they have no love for anybody

00:13:27.453 --> 00:13:33.449
and what they want is only material
things. This matter cannot give you joy,

00:13:33.449 --> 00:13:39.796
is already said in the Economics, if you
see, the law of Economics, the first
and the foremost is,

00:13:39.796 --> 00:13:48.110
that 'A want is satiable in particular
but not in general.'

00:13:48.110 --> 00:13:54.980
Means, nothing can satisfy your wants.
You will today asked say for a bicycle,

00:13:54.980 --> 00:14:00.429
tomorrow for a car, then for a house,
then for an aeroplane - I don't
know how it goes.

00:14:00.606 --> 00:14:07.666
So a person is never satisfied, who tries
to find joy in material things.

