00:14:52.452 --> 00:14:57.372
that most of the young people should
commit suicide - that's the only
way they can exist.

00:14:57.372 --> 00:15:02.644
That suggests one thing definitely,
that their movement towards the

00:15:02.644 --> 00:15:10.274
