to Spirit, trying to find out what should
they do to become the Spirit.

00:15:20.139 --> 00:15:24.729
Now we must know those people have
talked of the Spirit didn't tell lies.

00:15:24.729 --> 00:15:27.660
They didn't tell us lies - that is
first thing we must know.

00:15:27.660 --> 00:15:32.994
There are some people who say, "We
don't believe in God," - I think is a
sign of complete arrogance,

00:15:32.994 --> 00:15:39.745
is a sign of ignorance also that you
just say, "I don't believe in God."

00:15:40.440 --> 00:15:47.230
Is like a person who goes to a University
or school and there he goes and
tells his teacher,

00:15:47.230 --> 00:15:49.774
"I don't believe in this that this
can happen."

00:15:50.192 --> 00:15:59.162
If you are sensible and balanced person
and wise, then you can think it over,

00:15:59.162 --> 00:16:05.643
that why is it in the world today
there's a moral crisis, why we are
suffering so much?

00:16:05.643 --> 00:16:10.257
The reason is, we have given too much
importance to the material living.

00:16:10.257 --> 00:16:15.789
Too much importance. The material life
also cannot be a enjoyed without the
Spiritual life.

00:16:16.200 --> 00:16:21.562
Now, I'll tell you what happens when the
Kundalini rises above the Agnya Chakra,

00:16:21.562 --> 00:16:27.644
which is placed between the pitutary
and the pineal body in the
optic chiasma.

00:16:28.652 --> 00:16:35.182
The optic chiasma has got this very
important center.

00:16:35.662 --> 00:16:41.572
Now this important center cannot be
seen through a microscope or anything

00:16:41.572 --> 00:16:47.781
but it asserts and exerts this power
when you see the Kundalini rising.

00:16:47.781 --> 00:16:54.273
When the Kundalini rises, mostly it
stops at that point, which we call
as the Agnya chakra.

00:16:54.540 --> 00:16:59.200
You have seen now - yesterday you saw
so many people had this problem

00:16:59.200 --> 00:17:03.860
of their Kundalini stopping at the Nabhi
chakra or at the Agnya chakra.

00:17:03.860 --> 00:17:08.740
You can see clearly when it stops at the
Nabhi chakra, with your naked eye
you can see the pulsation

00:17:08.740 --> 00:17:13.612
of the Kundalini that rises and goes and
stops at liver or some places.

00:17:13.612 --> 00:17:16.163
but at the Agnya Chakra you
cannot see.

00:17:16.163 --> 00:17:19.116
When it stops at Agnya Chakra, it
also drops down.

00:17:19.720 --> 00:17:24.860
Now this Agnya chakra which is placed
between the pitutary and the pineal

00:17:24.860 --> 00:17:31.664
in the center of the optic chiasma, is
the one which is a very narrow gate,

00:17:31.664 --> 00:17:37.351
which is a very narrow gate through
which somebody had to pass through

00:17:37.351 --> 00:17:41.919
to prove that eternal life is to be sought.

00:17:41.952 --> 00:17:48.672
Like Krishna has said about eternal life,
'Nainam chidanti shastrani, nainam
dehti pavaka,'

00:17:48.719 --> 00:17:54.369
'Nainam chidanti shastrani, nainam
dehti pavaka, na chainam ....

00:18:00.649 --> 00:18:07.669
na shosayeti marut.' You see the thing
is, 'Na kledyantiyapo na shosayeti
marut.'

00:18:07.669 --> 00:18:16.902
The reason is, what he's trying to say is,
this cannot be killed, this cannot be
destroyed, this cannot be sucked in.'

00:18:16.902 --> 00:18:21.795
What is that? That is the Spiritual life,
that is the Eternal life that is within us.

00:18:21.795 --> 00:18:27.861
Now how do you do it? Where do you
get that eternal life which cannot be
crushed?

00:18:27.861 --> 00:18:30.448
If somebody had to show, what is that?

00:18:30.680 --> 00:18:39.460
Krishna has described it so clearly in
His lifetime that, 'You have to achieve
that eternal life, which I'm telling you.'

00:18:39.460 --> 00:18:43.821
So somebody had to come on this
earth, on this Agnya chakra to
work it out.

00:18:43.821 --> 00:18:49.615
In that I would say, that you should go
and read some of these treatise

00:18:50.490 --> 00:18:56.849
about Mahavishnu, which is described
by Markandeya.

00:18:56.849 --> 00:19:08.427
Markandeya is the person, who has very
clearly described the origin of
Mahavishnu.

00:19:08.606 --> 00:19:14.286
Mahavishnu was created by Shri
Radhaji. Shri Radhaji is the Mahalaxmi,

00:19:14.286 --> 00:19:17.954
is the Sushumna, is the
Parasympathetic Nervous System
within ourselves.

00:19:17.954 --> 00:19:22.717
She has created with Her own
will-power, this Mahavishnu.

00:19:22.844 --> 00:19:30.384
And this one was like an egg and half of
it became active and became
Mahavishnu

00:19:30.384 --> 00:19:37.476
and with that active Mahavishnu we can
cross through the Agnya chakra.

00:19:37.732 --> 00:19:44.182
As I told you before that we had ten
gurus who came on this earth

00:19:44.182 --> 00:19:50.418
and they represented the innocence of
the three, Brahma, Vishnu, Mahesha

00:19:50.418 --> 00:19:57.158
of Dattatreya and one of them was
Zoraster, another was
Mohammad Sahab

00:19:57.158 --> 00:20:06.600
and all these gurus represent those
qualities of innocence of these three
personalities, called as Dattatreya.

00:20:06.600 --> 00:20:13.627
And also told you how by understanding
these different gurus, we can produce

00:20:14.220 --> 00:20:17.612
effects even on our physical health.

00:20:17.612 --> 00:20:25.526
Like, we had a doctor who came all the
way from Iran and that day I was
very tired,

00:20:25.526 --> 00:20:35.612
very tired and I told him that 'You have
to become a Sikh gentleman, if you
want to become alright.'

00:20:35.612 --> 00:20:41.214
And, 'I cannot help you much because
you do not believe that there's
anybody else but Mohammad Sahab.'

00:20:41.214 --> 00:20:47.321
And he got very angry. I said, 'I'm really
very tired and in one sentence I want to
finish it because I'm really very tired.'

00:20:47.321 --> 00:20:51.431
