into you

00:28:03.249 --> 00:28:09.859
and you become like a box or like an
egg. Now this egg has to grow.

00:28:09.859 --> 00:28:17.445
When it is ready enough, then only, just
like we a call a Brahmin, a dwijah -

00:28:17.445 --> 00:28:23.328
a Brahmin who is not a dwijah, is called
abrahmin. In the shastras he is called as,

00:28:23.328 --> 00:28:28.385
a-brahmin - he's not a Brahmin, he's
a-brahmin. That 'a' has to go away

00:28:28.385 --> 00:28:40.131
