a-brahmin. So when this breaks,
this egg breaks into a new being,

00:28:40.131 --> 00:28:46.376
when you become a new being, you're
called a dwijah and a bird is also
called a dwijah,

00:28:46.376 --> 00:28:51.319
means, twice born. But there are many
people I met, they said, "We're
already twice born."

00:28:51.319 --> 00:28:53.791
