twice born."

00:28:53.870 --> 00:28:58.310
What do you mean by twice-born? You
cannot just give a certificate to yourself.

00:28:58.310 --> 00:29:04.842
If you're twice-born, then what is the
speciality? What do you get as a
twice-born personality?

00:29:04.842 --> 00:29:12.524
First of all, you should become
collectively conscious - means on your
Central Nervous System.

00:29:12.524 --> 00:29:17.538
Always, whatever you have evolved,
comes on your Central Nervous system.

00:29:17.538 --> 00:29:23.729
But now after realization, on your
Central Nervous system you should feel

00:29:24.737 --> 00:29:32.167
your own centres, the subtle centres
and you should feel the centres of
others. That's the minimum

00:29:32.167 --> 00:29:35.206
that should happen to a person,
who says who's a yogi.

00:29:35.206 --> 00:29:38.785
If he cannot say that, then he's just
giving him a certificate,

00:29:38.785 --> 00:29:41.981
like that, you can certify yourself that,
"I'm the Prime Minister of India,"

00:29:41.981 --> 00:29:47.249
but who's going to listen to you? This
self-certification is a very easy thing,

00:29:47.259 --> 00:29:52.454
as far as God is concerned and the
religion is concerned because there is
no law that people think

00:29:52.454 --> 00:29:59.391
can really guide them or can put them
in the prison, so they do the
way they like.

00:29:59.391 --> 00:30:07.507
Now we have to understand that there
is a life in this lifetime only -

00:30:07.507 --> 00:30:13.929
you're going to get a life which is in a
very different dimension,

00:30:13.929 --> 00:30:20.326
where your Spirit starts shining through
your attention, through your
Central Nervous System.

00:30:20.326 --> 00:30:24.240
Yesterday many people felt the cool
breeze. Now what is this cool breeze?

00:30:24.240 --> 00:30:32.223
This cool breeze is the Onkar Shakti,
is the Brahm Shakti of God, the
All-Pervading Power of God.

00:30:32.223 --> 00:30:37.829
The Power that converts or that
transforms a flower into a fruit.

00:30:38.890 --> 00:30:42.909
Till you become a fruit, we do not
separate the fruit from the tree.

00:30:42.909 --> 00:30:48.286
In the same way, till you become a
realized soul, you cannot have
that detachment.

00:30:48.286 --> 00:30:55.294
Those people who work at detachment
before realization, are really trying to
do a very immature thing.

00:30:55.294 --> 00:31:03.380
It doesn't work. Whence you are
matured enough, then only you can feel
the detachment completely

00:31:03.380 --> 00:31:06.870
and in that detachment you give, you
become dynamic.

00:31:06.870 --> 00:31:14.903
Like the sap in the tree, it rises, rises
and give it's energy, nourishment,
to every leaf,

00:31:14.903 --> 00:31:21.331
to every branch, to every flower, to
every fruit and it returns back, it doesn't
get attached to anyone.

00:31:21.331 --> 00:31:26.317
If anybody gets attached like that, we
can see in any tree - it does not -

00:31:26.317 --> 00:31:30.909
they're sensible because trees and
'pashu's' are in the 'pasha' of God

00:31:30.909 --> 00:31:32.834
so they are sensible thing - they
never get attached.

00:31:32.834 --> 00:31:37.570
But supposing like human-beings, they
get attached to one flower or to
one fruit,

00:31:37.619 --> 00:31:41.269
the whole tree will die and that fruit
will also die.

00:31:41.269 --> 00:31:45.199
But this is what we do not realize, when
we get attached to our children,

00:31:45.199 --> 00:31:51.190
get attached to one person or attached
to this and attached to that, attached
to material thing.

00:31:51.190 --> 00:31:57.807
