Question: What is Your view about
rebirth in different animal forms?

00:38:52.413 --> 00:38:55.573
Shri Mataji: Rebirth in different?
Sahaj yogi: In different animal forms.

00:38:56.233 --> 00:39:02.403
Sahaja Yogi: How after man dies he will
be born as an animal or as a
human being.

00:39:02.487 --> 00:39:07.407
Seeker: Life after death.
Shri Mataji: Now why are you worried
about death, I'm talking about life.

00:39:08.386 --> 00:39:12.426
This is a typical Indian mind, I tell you.
[UNCLEAR]

00:39:12.476 --> 00:39:17.224
First of all they'll come and ask,
"Mother, was I anything in last life?"

00:39:18.599 --> 00:39:26.719
"Then , what was I?" I said, "Baba, why
are you worried? To Me you are My son,
you better get your realization."

00:39:26.719 --> 00:39:34.853
We have to be in the present. We have
to be in the present. Once it's finished,
then future doesn't exist.

00:39:34.853 --> 00:39:37.365
We have to be in the present.

00:39:40.377 --> 00:39:43.457
Question: Is 'prakriti' and 'purusha' one?

00:39:43.457 --> 00:39:49.441
Shri Mataji: Of course. It's like moon
and moonlight, sun and sunlight.

00:39:52.722 --> 00:39:58.992
But when the Prakriti creates, the
Purusha watches.

00:40:15.071 --> 00:40:21.291
Question: Inspite of my efforts for the
last few days, I have not had been
inception of my kundalini.

00:40:21.291 --> 00:40:26.113
Can I have Your touch to clear my
chakras?

00:40:26.113 --> 00:40:32.970
Shri Mataji: Alright. When you'll come
down you will have this. I'll work hard
for that. We'll work it out.

00:40:33.729 --> 00:40:39.759
Question: It is extremely typical to
become a lady saint. Please comment.

00:40:41.044 --> 00:40:44.964
Shri Mataji: I mean, I'm not a saint,
I'm a Mother, that's all.

00:40:44.989 --> 00:40:52.139
It's very easy for Me to become the
Mother. If your Kundalini is the Mother,
I'm also a Mother.

00:40:53.014 --> 00:40:58.854
Is the easiest thing to be a Mother. I do
not claim to be a saint or anything
like that.

00:40:58.909 --> 00:41:03.459
But lady is always a sage so she
cannot become a sanyasi.

00:41:05.848 --> 00:41:08.638
A woman's position is like that.

00:41:11.263 --> 00:41:15.643
A mother, who looks after the child,
gives all her attention to the child,

00:41:15.643 --> 00:41:22.764
is already in saintlihood actually. But
we Indians, we think that only men
can become saints;

00:41:22.764 --> 00:41:25.536
Naturally, those who are not, have to
become saints.

00:41:36.860 --> 00:41:40.150
Question: Can ladies chant the
Gayatri Mantra?

00:41:40.354 --> 00:41:44.454
Shri Mataji: Haan. No one should chant
without understanding.

00:41:44.553 --> 00:41:49.793
Now, Gayatri mantra is to be chanted
by people who are depressed in life,

00:41:50.333 --> 00:41:56.393
who feel nervous in life, who are
left-sided. So ladies, some of the
ladies have to do.

00:41:57.199 --> 00:42:01.939
And those men who are like that, also
have to do. But those who are already

00:42:01.939 --> 00:42:05.714
riding a high horse, should stop
chanting Gayatri mantra.

00:42:12.229 --> 00:42:18.049
Question: My son is suffering from
asthma. What should I do? He is
ten years old.

00:42:18.049 --> 00:42:22.516
Shri Mataji: Alright. Certainly Sahaja
Yoga can cure to a child. You have to

00:42:22.516 --> 00:42:26.577
come to our center and they will
tell you what is to be done.

00:42:26.577 --> 00:42:31.416
All the individual questions should be
sorted out in the center individually.

00:42:31.530 --> 00:42:37.150
We can pay attention individually. We
have doctors here, we have other
people, they can look after you.

00:42:40.589 --> 00:42:47.519
Question: Is it the mother which we,
which has no beginning and end.
Therefore, how we call it?

00:42:50.058 --> 00:42:51.679
Shri Mataji: Is it the mother?

00:42:51.679 --> 00:42:56.714
Sahaja Yogi: Is it the mother which has
no beginning and end therefore,
how we call it?

00:42:56.714 --> 00:43:01.039
Shri Mataji: Mother, that's all. Mother
is [UNCLEAR]

00:43:05.271 --> 00:43:11.381
Question: I have been feeling
intoxicated since two days, something
different. What is this feeling?

00:43:12.653 --> 00:43:15.913
श्री माताजी: जब मस्त हुए फिर क्या बोलें ?
[Shri Mataji: What can I say when I'm
in ecstasy!]

00:43:22.845 --> 00:43:31.455
Question: A chandan has been
recreated for the forehead which
is white and not red

00:43:32.451 --> 00:43:37.011
Shri Mataji: There are two types of
chandanas - white and the red

00:43:37.011 --> 00:43:41.406
and the red is to be used for people
who are left-sided, depressive

00:43:41.406 --> 00:43:47.158
but people who are aggressive, are
people who are right-sided. They have
to use white chandanas.

00:43:48.901 --> 00:43:52.211
Question: Can You throw light for
what are we born?

00:43:52.794 --> 00:43:55.654
Shri Mataji: We are born to be innocent.

00:43:55.654 --> 00:44:00.740
We are born to be the citizens of God
[UNCLEAR]

00:44:00.740 --> 00:44:05.922
To enter into His Kingdom, to enjoy all
these blessings and glories.

00:44:05.922 --> 00:44:16.205
Like a very gracious Father, He's invited
you and He wants to grant all that is
possible for His children.

00:44:20.181 --> 00:44:25.571
Sahaja Yogi: On behalf of all the Delhi
Sahaja yogies, we cordially invite you

00:44:25.571 --> 00:44:31.426
to celebrate Shri Mataji's birthday on
the 20th. It is a great honor that

00:44:31.426 --> 00:44:37.981
Shri Mataji has agreed to stay this extra
few days so that we are able to

00:44:37.981 --> 00:44:43.104
be present for this auspicious occasion.
You're all invited and we hope

00:44:43.104 --> 00:44:49.467
that you will all come and bring others
also to celebrate and make this a
great success. Thank You!

00:44:49.467 --> 00:44:54.267
Now Shri Mataji will give realization.
[APPLAUSE]

00:45:22.426 --> 00:45:28.316
Question: Mother, You have told about
Kundalini jagran but how can it
be achieved?

00:45:28.316 --> 00:45:35.202
I want a practical of this.
Shri Mataji: Alright, we'll have it now.
Practical

00:45:37.805 --> 00:45:42.745
Now the people who are standing,
can sit down, can come forward
and sit down.

00:45:42.745 --> 00:45:48.665
Everybody should sit down. You'll be
seated, comfortably.

00:45:50.341 --> 00:45:52.861
Please be seated comfortably.

00:46:11.166 --> 00:46:16.586
पहाड़ की जैसी कुण्डलिनी उठानी पड़ती है - करें क्या ? हाँ।
[Kundalini, similar to a mountain, has to
be lifted, what to do? Yes.]

00:46:24.266 --> 00:46:30.176
It's a very simple process. As I told you
that we have Sympathetic endings

00:46:30.176 --> 00:46:38.101
on these five fingers, six and seven
centers on the left and same way, five,
six and seven centers.

00:46:38.152 --> 00:46:48.632
Now when you put your hands like this,
the chaitanya goes, passes through

00:46:48.632 --> 00:46:55.736
your Sympathetic nerve endings and
informs, as I told you, Shri Ganesha
on the Muladhara.

00:46:57.630 --> 00:47:06.830
As a result of that Kundalini ascends.
For that, is very simple,

00:47:06.856 --> 00:47:10.366
you have a cooperate with Me a little
bit and it will work out.

00:47:10.366 --> 00:47:17.255
It can work out on anyone. There's no
age problem, no problem at all.

00:47:17.255 --> 00:47:21.439
It works out very easily. Now first of
all, take out your shoes -

00:47:21.439 --> 00:47:26.608
is the help because this Mother Earth is
the one, which is represented within us

00:47:26.608 --> 00:47:34.438
in the Sacrum bone as Kundalini.
Please take out your shoes and put your
hands towards Me.

00:47:41.030 --> 00:47:48.840
Now try to follow what I tell you. Is very,
very simple but try to follow. Is very
simple.

00:47:50.380 --> 00:47:58.400
That first of all, you have to thank your
Mother Earth or this yog bhumi of India

00:47:58.400 --> 00:48:08.158
for giving you birth in this great country
and that request Her that She will bless
you at this time of your realization.

00:48:08.184 --> 00:48:14.964
So, with complete heart in that prayer,
you ask Her blessings three times.

00:48:19.086 --> 00:48:29.106
तीन बार अपनी मातृभूमि के प्रति श्रद्धांजलि अर्पित
करते हुए आप उनसे आशीर्वाद माँगें कि,

00:48:29.106 --> 00:48:35.475
"हे माँ इस समय जब कि हमारा मोक्ष का क्षण
है, आप हमें आशीर्वादित करिए।"

00:48:37.246 --> 00:48:42.066
ऐसे तीन बार कहें - पूर्ण ह्रदय से।

00:48:54.076 --> 00:49:01.696
अब सीधी बात और एक है, कि हमें अपने अंदर
बसा हुआ इनोसेंस(अबोधिता) जो है,

00:49:01.789 --> 00:49:09.369
जो कि श्री गणेश के रूप में है, उससे संरक्षण
माँगना होगा। इससे ये कहें कि,

00:49:09.369 --> 00:49:17.222
"हे गणेश, हे श्री गणेश, आप इस मोक्ष क्षण
में हमारा संरक्षण करिए।" तीन बार कहें।

00:49:17.696 --> 00:49:24.446
Please request Shri Ganesha as a prayer
offered to Him that, "O Shri Ganesha,

00:49:24.446 --> 00:49:31.127
at this time of our ascent, please
protect me." Say it thrice.

00:49:44.589 --> 00:49:55.029
Now put your left hand on your lap
comfortably. Left hand represents
the Ichcha shakti,

00:49:55.029 --> 00:50:02.430
the power of desire that your desire is
of your self-realization and the right
hand on your heart.

00:50:03.446 --> 00:50:09.226
The right hand represents your kriya
shakti, is the power of action.

00:50:09.226 --> 00:50:13.852
So left hand should be comfortably
placed on your lap.

00:50:14.957 --> 00:50:23.837
अपने गोद में लेफ्ट हैंड आप आराम से रख
लीजिए। इससे इच्छा शक्ति प्रदर्शित होगी।

00:50:23.962 --> 00:50:30.762
और राइट हैंड अपने ह्रदय पे रख लें।
इस ह्रदय में आत्मा का वास है।

00:50:31.096 --> 00:50:35.746
और राइट हैंड जो है वो क्रिया शक्ति
प्रदर्शित कर रहा है।

00:50:38.106 --> 00:50:47.656
ह्रदय पे रख कर के आप पूर्ण विश्वास से एक
सवाल पूछें, मन में पूछें कि, "माँ क्या मैं आत्मा हूँ?"

00:50:49.633 --> 00:50:56.003
बहुत से लोग जो पहले से आ रहे हैं, उनको
आलरेडी हाथ में ठंडक हवा आ रही है।

00:50:56.434 --> 00:51:03.284
लेकिन तो भी मैं कहूँगी कि सब लोग पैर ज़मीन
पर रखें तो अच्छा रहेगा, क्योंकि माँ की
बड़ी मदद होती है इसमें।

00:51:06.634 --> 00:51:13.344
"क्या मैं आत्मा हूँ। माँ, क्या मैं आत्मा हूँ?"

00:51:13.465 --> 00:51:18.195
Now ask the question in your heart,
"Mother, am I the Spirit?"

00:51:19.152 --> 00:51:27.382
Please ask this question thrice. This is
just to clear your mind about it.

00:51:29.655 --> 00:51:36.975
It's like a port of a computer.
When you ask the question to the
computer, the answer comes.

00:51:37.255 --> 00:51:49.075
So, ask the question. For people who
suffer from over-active heart

00:51:49.075 --> 00:51:58.334
and all the consequent diseases out of
that should always use this as a mantra
saying, "Mother, I am the Spirit."

00:52:01.078 --> 00:52:06.658
Now put this right hand on the stomach
on the left hand side.

00:52:07.374 --> 00:52:16.074
Now here the chakra of guru tatwa
works up. The guru tatwa,

00:52:16.074 --> 00:52:20.717
the principle of guru within you works
out on the left hand side of your
stomach.

00:52:21.600 --> 00:52:28.470
As you are the Spirit, you have to be
your own guru. So you have to say,

00:52:28.567 --> 00:52:31.247
"Mother, am I my own guru?"

00:52:32.054 --> 00:52:36.964
अब राइट हैंड अपने पेट पर आप लेफ्ट
साइड में रख लीजिए।

00:52:39.571 --> 00:52:46.641
और इसके बाद आप ये सवाल पूछिए कि,
"माँ क्या मैं स्वयं का गुरु हूँ?"

00:52:46.641 --> 00:52:56.924
क्योंकि ये गुरु तत्व का सेंटर है, उसका केंद्र है;
और क्योंकि आपने पहला सवाल पूछा था,
कि क्या आप आत्मा हैं।

00:52:56.924 --> 00:53:05.659
आपने उसी के क्रमुक आपने जो दूसरा सवाल है
वो पूछा कि, "माँ क्या मैं स्वयं का गुरु हूँ?"
ये तीन बार पूछिए।

00:53:11.233 --> 00:53:20.013
इसके पूछने के बाद आप इस राइट हैंड को फिर
नीचे की तरफ ले जाएँ। पेट पर नीचे की
तरफ रखें।

00:53:20.479 --> 00:53:32.309
इस जगह जो स्वाधिष्ठान चक्र है, जो स्वाधिष्ठान चक्र
है, वो यहाँ पर शुद्ध विद्या प्रदान करता है,
आपको शुद्ध विद्या देता है।

00:53:32.309 --> 00:53:39.945
शुद्ध विद्या वो विद्या है जिससे आप परमात्मा का
दिया हुआ ये जो आशीर्वाद है,

00:53:39.945 --> 00:53:49.573
जो आपका आत्मसाक्षात्कार है, उसे आप प्लावित
कर सकते हैं, उसे आप इस्तेमाल कर सकते हैं।

00:53:50.004 --> 00:53:53.774
आप ये जान सकते हैं कि परमात्मा के
कायदे-कानून क्या हैं।

00:53:53.774 --> 00:53:59.898
इसी एक शुद्ध विद्या से ही आप सारा परमात्मा के
बारे में सारा ज्ञान प्राप्त कर सकते हैं।

00:53:59.898 --> 00:54:08.115
शुद्ध विद्या माने वो तकनीक, वो तंत्र जिससे आप
ये जान लें कि परमात्मा की शक्ति क्या है

00:54:08.115 --> 00:54:12.183
और उसे किस तरह से इस्तेमाल करना चाहिए।
इसीलिए इसे शुद्ध विद्या कहते हैं।

00:54:12.483 --> 00:54:19.593
क्योंकि बिल्कुल ये अब्सोल्यूट है, एकांकी
है, इससे दूसरा कोई उसका पर्याय नहीं है -
पर्याय रहित।

00:54:20.369 --> 00:54:27.439
Putting your hand on the lower side of
the abdomen, you have to say,

00:54:29.372 --> 00:54:35.632
"Mother, please give me Pure
Knowledge, Shuddh Vidya."

00:54:35.744 --> 00:54:40.414
Shuddh Vidya means the
Pure Knowledge, means the knowledge

00:54:40.414 --> 00:54:50.030
about all the laws and regulations of
God's energy, all the technique of
handling that energy

00:54:50.030 --> 00:54:56.054
and all the knowledge about the
Spirit - is the Shuddh Vidya,

00:54:56.054 --> 00:55:02.647
so please ask six times, "Mother, give
me Shuddh Vidya, give me
Pure Knowledge."

00:55:02.647 --> 00:55:07.096
आप भी कहें, "कृपया माँ मुझे शुद्ध विद्या दीजिए,"
छह बार।

00:55:07.096 --> 00:55:10.829
ये आपके माँगे बगैर मैं ज़बरदस्ती नहीं
कर सकती।

00:55:10.829 --> 00:55:14.975
I cannot force it on you because you
are independent.

00:55:14.975 --> 00:55:23.354
आप स्वतंत्र हैं। आप जब तक इसे माँगेगे
नहीं, मैं ये दे नहीं सकती, सो कहिए,
"माँ मुझे आप शुद्ध विद्या दीजिए।"

00:55:44.818 --> 00:55:50.658
छह बार कहिए क्योंकि इसके छह,
इसकी छह कलियाँ हैं।

00:55:50.658 --> 00:55:54.619
इस चक्र की छह कलियाँ हैं इसलिए इसे
छह बार कहिए।

00:56:02.062 --> 00:56:08.142
अब इसके बाद हम लोगों को अपनी कुण्डलिनी
पर प्रभाव डाल सकते हैं

00:56:08.142 --> 00:56:13.916
और अलग अलग एक एक चक्र को खोलते हुए
हम ऊपर जा सकते हैं। सब काम
लेफ्ट साइड में होगा।

00:56:13.916 --> 00:56:19.890
You have to now work on the left hand
side and now you can control the
Kundalini's ascent.

00:56:19.890 --> 00:56:27.270
So you start now to the next chakra on
the stomach on the left hand side
of the Guru tatwa.

00:56:28.024 --> 00:56:36.044
At this point, with full confidence, you
please say that, "Mother I am my
own master, I am my own guru."

00:56:49.936 --> 00:56:55.056
Say that ten times for there are ten
principles of guru.

00:56:57.976 --> 00:57:03.411
Now put the full attention onto it.

00:57:03.411 --> 00:57:09.174
दस मर्तबा आप कहिए पूर्ण विश्वास के साथ
कि, "माँ, मैं स्वयं का गुरु हूँ।"

00:57:09.174 --> 00:57:18.056
इस वक्त आप अपना हाथ गुरु तत्व के चक्र पे
रखें, जो कि लेफ्ट हैंड आपने लेफ्ट साइड में
पेट पर ऊपर की ओर रखा हुआ है।

00:57:26.557 --> 00:57:36.027
अब इस हाथ को आप ह्रदय पर ले जाएँ।
Take this hand to your heart, please.

00:57:36.237 --> 00:57:44.267
ह्रदय पर ले जा कर के, यहाँ पर आपको पूर्ण
विश्वास से अब कहना होगा कि, "माँ, मैं आत्मा हूँ।"

00:57:44.886 --> 00:57:54.506
Please put your hand on the heart and
say with full assertion and full faith in
yourself that, "Mother, I am the Spirit."

00:57:54.506 --> 00:58:01.794
Please say this twelve times because
this centre has got twelve petals.

00:58:02.486 --> 00:58:07.656
बारह मर्तबा आप कहिए कि, "माँ मैं आत्मा हूँ।"

00:58:18.319 --> 00:58:22.249
अब बारह मर्तबा पूरे मन से कहें।

00:58:26.463 --> 00:58:36.423
आप अगर आत्मा हैं तो आप निर्दोष हैं। बहुत
से लोग अपने तो बहुत दोषमय समझते हैं।

00:58:36.423 --> 00:58:42.984
हर समय दोष अपने निकालते रहते हैं अपने
को नीचे गिराते हैं और कहते हैं कि, "मैंने
ये दोष किया वो दोष किया।"

00:58:42.984 --> 00:58:46.604
इससे आपकी लेफ्ट नाभि पकड़ जाती है
जिससे एनजाइना जैसी बीमारियाँ होतीं हैं।

00:58:46.889 --> 00:58:53.419
इसलिए अब आप अपना हाथ उठा करके
लेफ्ट विशुद्धि पर रखें सामने की तरफ से

00:58:53.419 --> 00:58:57.579
यहाँ पर जहाँ पर कि आपका कन्धा
और गर्दन मिलते हैं।

00:58:57.579 --> 00:59:02.476
ज़ोर से वहाँ पकड़ें, उँगलियाँ पीछे की ओर
ले जाएँऔर ज़ोर से पकड़ कर के खींचें।

00:59:05.275 --> 00:59:11.005
इस जगह आपको ये कहना चाहिए सोलह मर्तबा
क्योंकि श्री कृष्ण का ये लेफ्ट साइड है

00:59:11.033 --> 00:59:21.323
कि, "माँ, मैं आत्मा हूँ और मैं निर्दोष हूँ।"
पूरे विश्वास के साथ कहिए। सोलह मर्तबा।

00:59:22.846 --> 00:59:28.996
पूरा विश्वास रखिए क्योंकि परमात्मा जो है
वो प्रेम का सागर है, आनंद का सागर है,

00:59:28.996 --> 00:59:38.896
दया का सागर है, पर सबसे अधिक वो क्षमा का
सागर है। वो क्षमा का सागर है - रेहमत, रहीम।

00:59:41.763 --> 00:59:53.243
हाँ! सोलह मर्तबा कहें।

00:59:53.243 --> 01:00:00.591
Please say it sixteen times that,
"Mother, I am the Spirit and I'm
not guilty."

01:00:00.591 --> 01:00:05.302
Please say it sixteen times, "Mother,
I am the Spirit and I'm not guilty."

01:00:33.090 --> 01:00:43.110
Now, raise this right hand onto your
forehead across. Now here is the
Agnya chakra.

01:00:43.140 --> 01:00:50.060
Press your forehead. Now say,
"Mother, I forgive everyone."

01:00:50.456 --> 01:00:56.486
While saying this you must remember,
first of all you must forgive yourself.

01:00:56.486 --> 01:01:03.352
You say, "Mother, I forgive everyone,
I forgive everyone."

01:01:03.993 --> 01:01:13.893
इस हाथ को ऊपर उठा करके अपने भाल प्रदेश
पर संभाल रखें। संभाल - पूरी तरह से पकड़ के।

01:01:14.606 --> 01:01:19.676
अपना हाथ सर पे माथे पर इस तरह से रखें
जैसे आड़ा और उसको दबा कर

01:01:19.676 --> 01:01:24.250
माथे को पकड़ें और इस जगह आप कहें
कि, "माँ, मैंने सब को क्षमा कर दी है।"

01:01:24.797 --> 01:01:29.807
बहुत से लोग कहते हैं कि, "माँ क्षमा करना बहुत
कठिन है," लेकिन अगर आप क्षमा नहीं कर रहे हैं,

01:01:29.807 --> 01:01:36.926
तो आप अपने को ही तो तकलीफ दे रहें हैं। ये
समझ लेना चाहिए, इसलिए कृपया कहिए कि,
"माँ, मैंने सब को क्षमा कर दी है।"

01:01:44.987 --> 01:01:49.907
अब ये हाथ आप पीछे की ओर ले जाएँ,
जो सर को पकड़ लीजिए पीछे से।

01:01:49.907 --> 01:01:56.637
पीछे में जो हिस्सा बाहर की ओर काफी निकला
हुआ रहता है, उसे आप पकड़ लें।

01:01:57.968 --> 01:02:04.698
Please put your hand on the backside
of your head and try to hold it
very tight.

01:02:05.770 --> 01:02:11.420
अब आप निर्दोष हैं, बिल्कुल निर्दोष हैं
लेकिन आपको ये कहना होगा कि,

01:02:11.420 --> 01:02:16.529
"मुझसे अगर कोई गलती हो गयी हो, तो परमात्मा
मुझे क्षमा करें।" ऐसे तीन बार कहें।

01:02:16.529 --> 01:02:21.907
आप हालाँकि निर्दोष हैं, उसमें कोई दोष नहीं, पर
अगर कोई गलती हो गई हो तो उसे क्षमा कर दें।

01:02:28.563 --> 01:02:32.783
पूर्ण ह्रदय से कहें। नतमस्तक होकर के नम्र
भाव से कहें।

01:02:32.783 --> 01:02:36.533
Now you have to say when you put
your hand on the back that,

01:02:36.533 --> 01:02:40.901
"Please forgive me if I have done any
mistakes," to God.

01:02:41.613 --> 01:02:45.733
To God Almighty you have to ask for
forgiveness, but you are not guilty,

01:02:45.733 --> 01:02:51.653
you're not guilty. Don't feel guilty about
it. Just say that without feeling guilty.

01:02:58.332 --> 01:03:03.642
Now, on top of the head, put your
hand, right hand on top of your head,

01:03:03.642 --> 01:03:09.389
on the fontanel bone area and press it
with palm and move it in a
clockwise manner.

01:03:09.389 --> 01:03:17.220
अब अपने तालू पर अपना हाथ रखें।
हाथ का मतलब ये है कि हथेली

01:03:17.220 --> 01:03:25.640
और उसको आप इस तरह से दबाइए और
घुमाइए जैसे कि घडी के काँटे घूमते हैं।

01:03:25.640 --> 01:03:31.681
इसको घुमाते वक्त यहाँ सात चक्र हैं, जिसके
बारे में मैं बताऊँगी परसों आपसे, जो सहस्त्रार है।

01:03:31.897 --> 01:03:39.427
इस सात चक्रों के लिए आप सात बार कहिए कि,
"माँ मुझे आत्मसाक्षात्कार दीजिए।"

01:03:39.427 --> 01:03:47.372
यहाँ पर भी मैं रुक जातीं हूँ, क्योंकि मेरी ऐसी कोई
इच्छा नहीं कि आपकी स्वतंत्रता को लाँघ जाऊँ।

01:03:47.372 --> 01:03:54.923
जो आदमी स्वयं स्वतंत्र नहीं है, वो परमात्मा का तंत्र
नहीं जान सकता और वो पूरी स्वतंत्रता भी
उपभोग नहीं कर सकता।

01:03:54.923 --> 01:04:00.979
इसलिए पूर्ण स्वतंत्रता में आपको कहना चाहिए
कि, "माँ मुझे आप यहाँ पर आत्मसाक्षातकार
दीजिए।"

01:04:04.241 --> 01:04:11.261
Please ask for your Self-realization.
I cannot cross your freedom

01:04:11.261 --> 01:04:15.443
so you have to ask for it, "Mother please
give me Self-realization."

01:04:15.443 --> 01:04:20.176
